    "(3) Ultra-large scale management and scheduling.",
    "The scale of data management and control continues to increase, providing multi-modal data management and scheduling of PB-level large data volumes; Support complex business requirements logic cumbersome, frequent interaction of modular management, to achieve complex business logic-oriented management scheduling; Massive data and highly complex algorithms drive the cloud platform to achieve unified management and control of more large-scale computing power.A variety of learning methods based on AI models and even large models can design and generate adaptive intelligent planning and scheduling policies based on training models for business needs to improve the scheduling superiority of large-scale resources.",
